about.title: Michael Napolitano
about.description:
Here at RE/MAX Edge, we believe in making the real estate journey an effortless, enjoyable experience for our clients. Whether you’re selling your home or looking to purchase the right one for you, we are here to act as a guiding hand throughout this endeavour. From empowering you with the right knowledge and resources to ensuring a smooth and successful close, we’ll be there every step of the way.

Our credentials speak for themselves: As the #1 brokerage in the Brooklyn MLS and ranked in the Top 10 of brokerages in Staten Island MLS, we’re proud experts in the NYC market. Combined with our access to the most up-to-date industry data, we’re able to assist you in maneuvering through this fast-paced market with ease. Our network of highly reputable attorneys, lenders, inspectors, and beyond are here to help you make an informed decision that is right for you.

Agents at RE/MAX Edge are supported by a diligent, highly-trained Operations Team! The resources, education, and care we offer gives them the boost they need to flourish in this competitive market. We go the extra mile to ensure that our agents are equipped to provide their clients with a pleasant end-to-end experience that is unique to RE/MAX Edge alone.

Selling or buying a home can be a complex process, but it doesn’t have to be. With us, you will have the edge you need!
